Introduction

ICU is a South Korean girl group under Liz Entertainment. The group will use an admission system, which means other members can be added along the way. They debuted on October 22nd, 2019.

On August 28, 2022, it was announced that Hayu had graduated from the group and will be joining Chic&I's. On November 16, 2022, it was announced that member Ella had graduated from the group. On March 5, 2024, it was announced that Chic&I's and WE-SAY member Loa joined ICU. On February 28, 2025, it was announced that Chae-i had graduated from ICU and would be active as a soloist.
